<div>
	<span style="font-size:16px;"><strong>资料简介：</strong></span></div>
<div>
	<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;">1996年，Java还只是一个新兴的、初出茅庐的编程语言。2004年3月24日Spring正式对外发布1.0版本。我在2009年开始接触Spring2.0版本，从此爱不释手。Spring的出现，恰如其名开启了全世界Java程序员的春天。如今，Spring已然成为一个生态，使用Spring简直就是一种享受。本书将结合本人多年的Spring使用经验，整理珍藏多年的学习笔记，采用类关系图和代码片段的形式，加以中文注释，通俗、生动、全面深入地剖析了Spring源码的重要细节。同时，本书也作为咕泡学院Java VIP高级课程的教案。要想练就"降龙十八掌”，先得修炼内功。本书用从设计模式开始讲解，希望可以帮助大家更好地理解Spring，让大家知其然，且知其所以然。&nbsp;</span></div>
<div>
	&nbsp;</div>
<div>
	<span style="font-size:16px;"><strong>资料目录：</strong></span></div>
<div>
	<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;">第1篇 Spring内功心法&nbsp;</span><br style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;">
	<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;">第1章 软件架构设计原则 2&nbsp;</span><br style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;">
	<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;">1.1 开闭原则 2&nbsp;</span><br style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;">
	<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;">1.2 依赖倒置原则 4&nbsp;</span><br style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;">
	<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;">1.3 单一职责原则 7&nbsp;</span><br style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;">
	<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;">1.4 接口隔离原则 10&nbsp;</span><br style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;">
	<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;">1.5 迪米特原则 12&nbsp;</span><br style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;">
	<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;">1.6 里氏替换原则 14&nbsp;</span><br style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;">
	<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;">1.7 合成复用原则 19&nbsp;</span><br style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;">
	<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;">1.8 设计原则总结 20&nbsp;</span><br style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;">
	<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;">第2章 Spring中常用的设计模式 21&nbsp;</span><br style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;">
	<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;">2.1 为什么要从设计模式开始 21&nbsp;</span><br style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;">
	<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;">2.1.1 写出优雅的代码 22&nbsp;</span><br style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;">
	<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;">2.1.2 更好地重构项目 24&nbsp;</span><br style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;">
	<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;">2.1.3 经典框架都在用设计模式解决问题 36&nbsp;</span><br style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;">
	<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;">2.2 工厂模式详解 36&nbsp;</span><br style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;">

		21.26 请解释Spring中的IoC容器 543&nbsp;<br>
		21.27 在Spring中可以注入null或空字符串吗 543&nbsp;<br>
		<br>
		&nbsp;</div>

<a href="http://www.137zw.com" target="_blank"></a><a href="http://www.137zw.com/forum-59-1.html" target="_blank" style="color: #F00;">java</a><font face="Tahoma"><font size="2"><font color="#000000">自学网（</font><font color="#336699">www.137zw.com</font><font color="#000000">）-<a href="http://www.137zw.com/thread-426-1-1.html" target="_blank" style="color: #F00;">java论坛</a>，java电子书推荐：《Spring 5核心原理与30个类手写实战》</font></font></font><br>
<font face="Tahoma"><font size="2"><font color="#000000">java电子书推荐理由：</font></font></font><font color="#656565"><font face="Tahoma,">Spring的出现，恰如其名开启了全世界Java程序员的春天。如今，Spring已然成为一个生态，使用Spring简直就是一种享受。本书将结合本人多年的Spring使用经验，整理珍藏多年的学习笔记，采用类关系图和代码片段的形式，加以中文注释，通俗、生动、全面深入地剖析了Spring源码的重要细节。同时，本书也作为咕泡学院Java VIP高级课程的教案。要想练就"降龙十八掌”，先得修炼内功。本书用从设计模式开始讲解，希望可以帮助大家更好地理解Spring，让大家知其然，且知其所以然。</font></font><br>
<br>
<font size="2">作者：谭勇德（Tom）<br>
出版社：电子工业出版社<br>
出版时间：2019-07<br>
书籍价格：118.00元</font><br>

			<h1 style="word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; display: inline; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family:" microsoft="" color:="" background-color:=""><span style="word-wrap: break-word;">Spring 5核心原理与30个类手写实战+Spring
Boot编程思想核心篇pdf</span>&nbsp;<wbr></h1>
<span style="word-wrap: break-word; font-family:">&nbsp;<wbr></span>
<div><span style="word-wrap: break-word; font-family:"><font color="#596677">Spring 5核心原理与30个类手写实战+Spring Boot编程思想核心篇 pdf百度网盘 微服务软件架构
SpringBoot开发教程电子书pdf百度云下载&nbsp;<wbr>
&nbsp;<wbr></font><b style=""><font color="#FF3E0B">下载链接：</font></b></span><font color="#596677">http://www.137zw.com/thread-426-1-1.html</font>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft="" font-size:=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">《Spring
5核心原理与30个类手写实战》基于编程开发实践，不仅深度解析Spring
5的原理与新特性，更从环境准备、顶层结构设计、数据访问等方面一步步地推导出Spring的设计原理。在每个知识点上，均以大量的经典代码案例辅助讲解，使理论紧密联系实际。最后手写30个类，以体会Spring作者的创作过程，让每一位读者学以致用。</font></font></div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft="" font-size:=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">对于立志成为Java架构师的技术人员，以及对以Spring为核心的Java
Web开发感兴趣的计算机专业高校生、在职Java开发人员来说，本书是一本具备超强实战意义的技术升级指南。读者通过本书可以看源码不再“晕车”，轻松找到入口；系统学习设计思想，提高解决问题的效率；培养架构思维能力，以及自驱作者：小马哥
著</font></font></div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft="" font-size:="">
<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;"><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">出版社：电子工业出版社&nbsp;<wbr>&nbsp;<wbr></font></font></font></font></div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">书号：9787121360398</font></font></div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">出版时间：2019.3</font></font></div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">定价：118.0</font></font></div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">首先介绍微服务架构的基本概念，解释为什么业界纷纷选择Spring
Boot作为微服务的基础设施之一。了解了选择的理由后，接下里进入实践的部分，通过Hello World工程，简单地了解Spring
Boot 工程中的代码结构、依赖关系等。在初步印象的前提下，进一步地深入探讨Spring Boot
Web、数据、消息、校验、安全、日志、配置、测试等相关技术，最后探索自定义Spring Boot
Starter，分享相关的开发经验和注意事项。</font></font></div>

<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">9.6
下一站：理解SpringApplication 402</font></font></div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">第3部分
理解SpringApplication</font></font></div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">第10章
SpringApplication初始化阶段 405</font></font></div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">10.1
SpringApplication构造阶段 405</font></font></div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">10.1.1 理解SpringApplication主配置类
406</font></font></div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">10.1.2 SpringApplication的构造过程
410</font></font></div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">10.1.3 推断Web应用类型 411</font></font></div>

<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">10.2.1 自定义SpringApplication

// JavaScript Document
function goTopEx(){
 var obj=document.getElementById("goTopBtn");
 function getScrollTop(){
 return document.documentElement.scrollTop || document.body.scrollTop;
 }
 function setScrollTop(value){
 if(document.documentElement.scrollTop){
 document.documentElement.scrollTop=value;
 }else{
 document.body.scrollTop=value;
 }
 } 
 window.onscroll=function(){getScrollTop()>0?obj.style.display="":obj.style.display="none";
 var h=document.body.scrollHeight - getScrollTop() - obj.offsetTop - obj.offsetHeight;
 obj.style.bottom=0+"px";
 if(h<350){
 obj.style.bottom=340+"px";
 obj.style.top="auto";
 }
 }
 obj.onclick=function(){
 var goTop=setInterval(scrollMove,10);
 function scrollMove(){
 setScrollTop(getScrollTop()/1.1);
 if(getScrollTop()<1)clearInterval(goTop);
 }
 }
 }

        var myField;
        tag = ' ' + tag + ' ';
        if (document.getElementById('comment') && document.getElementById('comment').type == 'textarea') {
            myField = document.getElementById('comment');
        } else {
            return false;
        }
        if (document.selection) {
            myField.focus();
            sel = document.selection.createRange();
            sel.text = tag;
            myField.focus();
        }
        else if (myField.selectionStart || myField.selectionStart == '0') {
            var startPos = myField.selectionStart;
            var endPos = myField.selectionEnd;
            var cursorPos = endPos;
            myField.value = myField.value.substring(0, startPos)
                          + tag
                          + myField.value.substring(endPos, myField.value.length);
            cursorPos += tag.length;
            myField.focus();
            myField.selectionStart = cursorPos;
            myField.selectionEnd = cursorPos;
        }
        else {
            myField.value += tag;
            myField.focus();
        }
    }</script> <div id="respond" class="comment-respond"><h4 id="reply-title" class="comment-reply-title">发表评论 <small><a rel="nofollow" id="cancel-comment-reply-link" href="/a/343042#respond"                 <h1 class="title-article">Spring实战（中文4,5版） PDF含源码</h1>

         <div id="article_content" class="article_content clearfix" style="height: 1374px; overflow: hidden;">
            <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://csdnimg.cn/release/phoenix/template/css/ck_htmledit_views-833878f763.css">
                                        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://csdnimg.cn/release/phoenix/template/css/ck_htmledit_views-833878f763.css">
                <div class="htmledit_views" id="content_views">
                                            <div id="cnblogs_post_body" class="blogpost-body"><p><img src="http://www.xz577.com/uploads/1906/1-1Z604143121408.jpg" alt="Spring实战"></p>
<p>Spring实战</p>
<h3><a name="t0"></a><a name="t0"></a>读者评价</h3>
<p>看了一半后在做评论，物流速度挺快，正版行货，只是运输过程有点印记，但是想必大家和你关注内容，spring 4必之3更加关注的是使用注解做开发，对于初学者还是很有用，但是不排除对老用户也很有帮助。，全书分为四大部分我目前只看到第三部分不做过多评价。</p>
<p>全书知识深度较浅, 但非常权威(针对Sp5.0会有部分过时内容), 且能够在如此有限的篇幅中覆盖如此广阔的内容, 实属不易也实属罕见. 第1部分(DI、AOP):稳扎稳打,巩固基础; 第2部分(Web):MVC最传统, 最精华, 也是最实用的部分. 第3部分(存储):SQL、NoSQL, 各种酷炫吊炸天的操作, 优化(简化)到极致的存储代码... 不得不服! 另外@Secured保护方法调用也绝对一大亮点(如果你能够遇到一次安全故障, 你会深刻认同我的说法(⊙﹏⊙)b). 第4部分(集成):与各种企业级服务集成, 同步:RPC、Rest; 异步: MQ、WebSocket、Email;管理: JMX... 哪些曾经想所未想、见所未见的技术, Spring已经帮你实现, 给你提供工具了.</p>
<p>in action 系列的书就是读了特别容易上手。spring泡社区学习不够系统，读这本书就比较清楚了。主要还是侧着应用，读了一部分了，还是很推荐的，初学者拿来入门也是很好的。<br>这本书确实写的不错，书中举的例子也都比较有趣，骑士、奥特玛、小怪兽等等。每个核心的Spring技术点都解释得很容易懂，也能看出spring为何做出这样的设计。</p>
<h3><a name="t1"></a><a name="t1"></a>内容介绍</h3>
<p>本教程是Spring实战第5版英文原版，带源码，可结合Spring实战(第4版)进行阅读。</p>
<p>《Spring实战（第5版）》是经典的、畅销的Spring学习和实践指南。</p>
<p>本书适用于已具有一定Java 编程基础的读者，以及在Java 平台下进行各类软件开发的开发人员、测试人员，尤其适用于企业级Java 开发人员。本书既可以被刚开始学习Spring 的读者当作学习指南，也可以被那些想深入了解Spring 某方面功能的专业用户作为参考用书。</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h3><a name="t2"></a><a name="t2"></a>目录</h3>
<ul><li><ul><li>PART 1 FOUNDATIONAL SPRING 1</li>
<li>1 ■ Getting started with Spring 3</li>
<li>2 ■ Developing web applications 29</li>
<li>3 ■ Working with data 56</li>
<li>4 ■ Securing Spring 84</li>
<li>5 ■ Working with configuration properties 114</li>
<li>PART 2 INTEGRATED SPRING.135</li>
<li>6 ■ Creating REST services 137</li>
<li>7 ■ Consuming REST services 169</li>
<li>8 ■ Sending messages asynchronously 178</li>
<li>9 ■ Integrating Spring 209</li>
<li>PART 3 REACTIVE SPRING .239</li>
<li>10 ■ Introducing Reactor 241</li>
<li>11 ■ Developing reactive APIs 269</li>
<li>12 ■ Persisting data reactively 296</li>
<li>PART 4 CLOUD-NATIVE SPRING 321</li>
<li>13 ■ Discovering services 323</li>
<li>14 ■ Managing configuration 343</li>
<li>15 ■ Handling failure and latency 376</li>
<li>PART 5 DEPLOYED SPRING 393</li>
<li>16 ■ Working with Spring Boot Actuator 395</li>
<li>17 ■ Administering Spring 429</li>
<li>18 ■ Monitoring Spring with JMX 446</li>
<li>19 ■ Deploying Spring 454</li>
</ul></li></ul><p><img src="https://files.jb51.net/file_images/article/201906/20190606151947728.jpg" alt="" width="669" height="250"></p>
<p>资源链接：<span style="color:#ff0000;"><strong><a href="http://www.xz577.com/e/728.html" rel="nofollow"><span style="color:#ff0000;">http://www.xz577.com/e/728.html</span></a></strong></span></p></div>
<p>转载于:https://www.cnblogs.com/imaxiaobian/p/10984934.html</p>                                    </div>

<script>
    function watchBtnChange(flag, username) {
        $('span.blog-expert-button-follow').each(function(index) {
            if (flag) {
                if ($(this).attr("data-name") == username) {
                    $(this).html('<span class="hover-hide">已关注</span><span class="hover-show">取消</span>').removeClass('btn-red-follow').addClass('btn-gray-follow attented');
                }
            } else {
                if ($(this).attr("data-name") == username) {
                    $(this).html("关注").addClass('btn-red-follow').removeClass('btn-gray-follow attented');
                }
            }
        })
        if (username == $('p.csdn-tracking-statistics').attr("username")) {
            if (flag) {
                $('#btnAttent').addClass("attented").text("已关注").removeClass('btn-red-hollow').addClass('btn-gray-hollow');
                changeFans(1)
            } else {
                $('#btnAttent').text("关注").addClass('btn-red-hollow').removeClass('btn-gray-hollow attented');
                changeFans(-1)
            }
        }
    }
    function changeFans(num) {
        if ($('#fan').text().indexOf('+') < 0) {
            $('#fan').text(parseInt($('#fan').text()) + num);
        } else {
            $('#fanBox').attr('title', parseInt($('#fanBox').attr('title')) + num);
        }
    }
    window.csdn = window.csdn ? window.csdn : {};
    window.csdn.watchBtnChange = watchBtnChange;
</script><div class="csdn-tracking-statistics mb8 box-shadow" data-pid="blog" data-report-click="{&quot;mod&quot;:&quot;popu_4&quot;}" style="height:250px;">

                var myCaptcha1=_dx.Captcha(document.getElementById("test"), {
                    appKey: "captchadiscuzpluginbydingxiang2017",
                    style: "popup",
                    success: function (token) {
                        document.getElementById("dx_verify_token1").value=token;
                        myCaptcha1.hide();
                        lsSubmit();
                    }
                });
                var lsform = document.getElementById('lsform');
                var obj = document.createElement("input");
                obj.name = "dx_verify_token";
                obj.id = "dx_verify_token1";
                obj.type = "hidden";
                lsform.appendChild(obj);
                var button = document.forms[0].getElementsByTagName('button')[0];
                if (button.addEventListener) {   
                    button.addEventListener("click", function(e){
                        if(document.getElementById("ls_username").value!='' && document.getElementById("ls_password").value!=''){
                            e.preventDefault();
                            e.stopPropagation();
                            myCaptcha1.reload();
                            myCaptcha1.show();
                        }
                    }, false); 
                } else if (button.attachEvent) {
                    button.attachEvent("onclick", function(e){
                        if(document.getElementById("ls_username").value!='' && document.getElementById("ls_password").value!=''){
                            myCaptcha1.reload();
                            myCaptcha1.show();
                        }
                    }); 
                }

<script type="text/javascript">replyreload += ',' + 315442;</script><font face="Tahoma"><font size="2"><font color="#000000"><strong>java自学网（<a href="http://www.javazx.com/" target="_blank">www.javazx.com</a>）-java论坛，java电子书推荐：</strong>《 Spring 5开发大全》</font></font></font><br>
<font face="Tahoma"><font size="2"><font color="#000000"><strong>java电子书推荐理由：</strong></font></font></font><font color="#656565"><font face="&amp;quot;">前瞻 本书基于Spring 5版本编写，除讲解Spring 5新特性外，还介绍了REST 服务、响应式Web 开发、微服务设计、Spring Boot及Spring Cloud等方面的前瞻技术。 全面 本书全面介绍Spring框架，涵盖Spring核心、测试、数据访问、系统集成、Web开发、响应式编程及微服务等方面在内的26章的内容，可以说是Spring技术的“百科全书”。 实用 本书除了讲解Spring的理论知识外，还在每个知识点上辅以大量的实战案例，使理论可以联系实际，具备更强的可操作性。 简明 目录标注有“新功能”“实战”“难点”及“重点”等标识，方便读者做好知识点的归纳和总结。 权威 以Spring官方文档和Spring框架源码为主要参考依据，确保知识点的正确性。</font></font><font face="Tahoma"><font size="2"><font color="#000000"><br>
</font></font></font><br>
<font face="Tahoma"><font size="2"><font color="#000000"><strong>作者：</strong></font></font></font><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, Simsun"><font style="font-size:12px">柳伟卫</font></font></font><br>
<font face="Tahoma"><font size="2"><font color="#000000"><strong>出版社：</strong></font></font></font><font face="Verdana, Simsun"><font color="#000000"><font style="font-size:12px">北京大学出版社</font></font></font><br>

</script>

                var myCaptcha1=_dx.Captcha(document.getElementById("test"), {
                    appKey: "captchadiscuzpluginbydingxiang2017",
                    style: "popup",
                    success: function (token) {
                        document.getElementById("dx_verify_token1").value=token;
                        myCaptcha1.hide();
                        lsSubmit();
                    }
                });
                var lsform = document.getElementById('lsform');
                var obj = document.createElement("input");
                obj.name = "dx_verify_token";
                obj.id = "dx_verify_token1";
                obj.type = "hidden";
                lsform.appendChild(obj);
                var button = document.forms[0].getElementsByTagName('button')[0];
                if (button.addEventListener) {   
                    button.addEventListener("click", function(e){
                        if(document.getElementById("ls_username").value!='' && document.getElementById("ls_password").value!=''){
                            e.preventDefault();
                            e.stopPropagation();
                            myCaptcha1.reload();
                            myCaptcha1.show();
                        }
                    }, false); 
                } else if (button.attachEvent) {
                    button.attachEvent("onclick", function(e){
                        if(document.getElementById("ls_username").value!='' && document.getElementById("ls_password").value!=''){
                            myCaptcha1.reload();
                            myCaptcha1.show();
                        }
                    }); 
                }

<script type="text/javascript">replyreload += ',' + 385174;</script><font face="Tahoma"><font size="2"><font color="#000000"><strong>java自学网（<a href="http://www.javazx.com/" target="_blank">www.javazx.com</a>）-java论坛，java电子书推荐：</strong>《Spring 5核心原理与30个类手写实战》</font></font></font><br>
<font face="Tahoma"><font size="2"><font color="#000000"><strong>java电子书推荐理由：</strong></font></font></font><font color="#656565"><font face="&amp;quot;">Spring的出现，恰如其名开启了全世界Java程序员的春天。如今，Spring已然成为一个生态，使用Spring简直就是一种享受。本书将结合本人多年的Spring使用经验，整理珍藏多年的学习笔记，采用类关系图和代码片段的形式，加以中文注释，通俗、生动、全面深入地剖析了Spring源码的重要细节。同时，本书也作为咕泡学院Java VIP高级课程的教案。要想练就"降龙十八掌”，先得修炼内功。本书用从设计模式开始讲解，希望可以帮助大家更好地理解Spring，让大家知其然，且知其所以然。</font></font><font face="Tahoma"><font size="2"><font color="#000000"><br>
</font></font></font><br>
<font size="2"><font color="#000000"><font face="Tahoma"><strong>作者：</strong></font><font face="Verdana, Simsun">谭勇德</font><font face="Verdana, Simsun">（Tom）</font><br>
<font face="Tahoma"><strong>出版社：</strong></font><font face="Verdana, Simsun">电子工业出版社</font><br>

if(connect_autoshare == 1 && connect_isbind) {
_attachEvent(window, 'load', function(){
connect_share(connect_weibo_share_url, connect_openid);
});
}
</script>

	<span style="font-size:16px;"><strong>资料简介：</strong></span></div>
<div>
	<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;">1996年，Java还只是一个新兴的、初出茅庐的编程语言。2004年3月24日Spring正式对外发布1.0版本。我在2009年开始接触Spring2.0版本，从此爱不释手。Spring的出现，恰如其名开启了全世界Java程序员的春天。如今，Spring已然成为一个生态，使用Spring简直就是一种享受。本书将结合本人多年的Spring使用经验，整理珍藏多年的学习笔记，采用类关系图和代码片段的形式，加以中文注释，通俗、生动、全面深入地剖析了Spring源码的重要细节。同时，本书也作为咕泡学院Java VIP高级课程的教案。要想练就"降龙十八掌”，先得修炼内功。本书用从设计模式开始讲解，希望可以帮助大家更好地理解Spring，让大家知其然，且知其所以然。&nbsp;</span></div>
<div>
	&nbsp;</div>
<div>

		<div id="sina_keyword_ad_area2" class="articalContent   newfont_family">
			<h1 style="word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; display: inline; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family:" microsoft="" color:="" background-color:=""><span style="word-wrap: break-word;">Spring 5核心原理与30个类手写实战+Spring

<span style="word-wrap: break-word; font-family:">&nbsp;<wbr></span>
<div><span style="word-wrap: break-word; font-family:"><font color="#596677">Spring 5核心原理与30个类手写实战+Spring Boot编程思想核心篇 pdf百度网盘 微服务软件架构

<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft="" font-size:=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">《Spring
5核心原理与30个类手写实战》基于编程开发实践，不仅深度解析Spring
5的原理与新特性，更从环境准备、顶层结构设计、数据访问等方面一步步地推导出Spring的设计原理。在每个知识点上，均以大量的经典代码案例辅助讲解，使理论紧密联系实际。最后手写30个类，以体会Spring作者的创作过程，让每一位读者学以致用。</font></font></div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft="" font-size:=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">对于立志成为Java架构师的技术人员，以及对以Spring为核心的Java
Web开发感兴趣的计算机专业高校生、在职Java开发人员来说，本书是一本具备超强实战意义的技术升级指南。读者通过本书可以看源码不再“晕车”，轻松找到入口；系统学习设计思想，提高解决问题的效率；培养架构思维能力，以及自驱作者：小马哥
著</font></font></div>

<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">11.3.2 afterRefresh方法语义的变化
541</font></font></div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">11.3.3 Spring
Boot事件ApplicationStartedEvent语义的变化 543</font></font></div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">11.3.4
执行CommandLineRunner和ApplicationRunner 548</font></font></div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">第12章
SpringApplication结束阶段 550</font></font></div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">12.1
SpringApplication正常结束 550</font></font></div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">12.2
SpringApplication异常结束 555</font></font></div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">12.2.1 Spring Boot异常处理
556</font></font></div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">12.2.2 错误分析报告器——FailureAnalysisReporter
562</font></font></div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">12.2.3
自定义实现FailureAnalyzer和FailureAnalysisReporter
564</font></font></div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">12.2.4 Spring Boot
2.0重构handleRunFailure和reportFailure方法 566</font></font></div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">12.2.5 Spring Boot
2.0的SpringBootExceptionRepor<wbr>ter接口 567</font></font></div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">第13章
Spring Boot应用退出 571</font></font></div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">13.1
Spring Boot应用正常退出 572</font></font></div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">13.1.1 ExitCodeGenerator Bean生成退出码
572</font></font></div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">13.1.2 ExitCodeGenerator Bean退出码使用场景
576</font></font></div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">13.2
Spring Boot应用异常退出 580</font></font></div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">13.2.1 ExitCodeGenerator异常使用场景
582</font></font></div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">13.2.2 ExitCodeExceptionMapper
Bean映射异常与退出码 587</font></font></div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">13.2.3 退出码用于SpringApplication异常结束
589</font></font></div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">13.3
小马哥有话说 594</font></font></div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">13.4

            <script>
                var myCaptcha1=_dx.Captcha(document.getElementById("test"), {
                    appKey: "captchadiscuzpluginbydingxiang2017",
                    style: "popup",
                    success: function (token) {
                        document.getElementById("dx_verify_token1").value=token;
                        myCaptcha1.hide();
                        lsSubmit();
                    }
                });
                var lsform = document.getElementById('lsform');
                var obj = document.createElement("input");
                obj.name = "dx_verify_token";
                obj.id = "dx_verify_token1";
                obj.type = "hidden";
                lsform.appendChild(obj);
                var button = document.forms[0].getElementsByTagName('button')[0];
                if (button.addEventListener) {   
                    button.addEventListener("click", function(e){
                        if(document.getElementById("ls_username").value!='' && document.getElementById("ls_password").value!=''){
                            e.preventDefault();
                            e.stopPropagation();
                            myCaptcha1.reload();
                            myCaptcha1.show();
                        }
                    }, false); 
                } else if (button.attachEvent) {
                    button.attachEvent("onclick", function(e){
                        if(document.getElementById("ls_username").value!='' && document.getElementById("ls_password").value!=''){
                            myCaptcha1.reload();
                            myCaptcha1.show();
                        }
                    }); 
                }

<script type="text/javascript">replyreload += ',' + 385174;</script><font face="Tahoma"><font size="2"><font color="#000000"><strong>java自学网（<a href="http://www.javazx.com/" target="_blank">www.javazx.com</a>）-java论坛，java电子书推荐：</strong>《Spring 5核心原理与30个类手写实战》</font></font></font><br>
<font face="Tahoma"><font size="2"><font color="#000000"><strong>java电子书推荐理由：</strong></font></font></font><font color="#656565"><font face="&amp;quot;">Spring的出现，恰如其名开启了全世界Java程序员的春天。如今，Spring已然成为一个生态，使用Spring简直就是一种享受。本书将结合本人多年的Spring使用经验，整理珍藏多年的学习笔记，采用类关系图和代码片段的形式，加以中文注释，通俗、生动、全面深入地剖析了Spring源码的重要细节。同时，本书也作为咕泡学院Java VIP高级课程的教案。要想练就"降龙十八掌”，先得修炼内功。本书用从设计模式开始讲解，希望可以帮助大家更好地理解Spring，让大家知其然，且知其所以然。</font></font><font face="Tahoma"><font size="2"><font color="#000000"><br>
</font></font></font><br>
<font size="2"><font color="#000000"><font face="Tahoma"><strong>作者：</strong></font><font face="Verdana, Simsun">谭勇德</font><font face="Verdana, Simsun">（Tom）</font><br>
<font face="Tahoma"><strong>出版社：</strong></font><font face="Verdana, Simsun">电子工业出版社</font><br>

<div>
	<span style="font-size:16px;"><strong>资料简介：</strong></span></div>
<div>
	<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;">1996年，Java还只是一个新兴的、初出茅庐的编程语言。2004年3月24日Spring正式对外发布1.0版本。我在2009年开始接触Spring2.0版本，从此爱不释手。Spring的出现，恰如其名开启了全世界Java程序员的春天。如今，Spring已然成为一个生态，使用Spring简直就是一种享受。本书将结合本人多年的Spring使用经验，整理珍藏多年的学习笔记，采用类关系图和代码片段的形式，加以中文注释，通俗、生动、全面深入地剖析了Spring源码的重要细节。同时，本书也作为咕泡学院Java VIP高级课程的教案。要想练就"降龙十八掌”，先得修炼内功。本书用从设计模式开始讲解，希望可以帮助大家更好地理解Spring，让大家知其然，且知其所以然。&nbsp;</span></div>
<div>
	&nbsp;</div>

	<div id="articlebody" class="artical" favmd5="{&quot;6744fbbc0102ym70&quot;:&quot;f61749d0b303a46a568077b14d4b74bb&quot;}">
		<div class="articalTitle"> 
			
								<h2 id="t_6744fbbc0102ym70" class="titName SG_txta">Spring5核心原理与30个类手写实战+SpringBoot编程思想核心篇pdf</h2>
			
					<span class="time SG_txtc">(2019-10-11 14:01:44)</span><div class="turnBoxzz"><a href="javascript:;" class="SG_aBtn SG_aBtn_ico SG_turn" action-type="reblog" action-data="{srcBlog:1, blogId:'6744fbbc0102ym70'}"><cite><img class="SG_icon SG_icon111" src="http://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/common/sg_trans.gif" width="15" height="15" align="absmiddle">转载<em class="arrow">▼</em></cite></a></div>		</div>

						<!-- 正文开始 -->
		<div id="sina_keyword_ad_area2" class="articalContent   newfont_family">
			<h1 style="word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; display: inline; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family:" microsoft="" color:="" background-color:=""><span style="word-wrap: break-word;">Spring 5核心原理与30个类手写实战+Spring
Boot编程思想核心篇pdf</span>&nbsp;<wbr></h1>
<span style="word-wrap: break-word; font-family:">&nbsp;<wbr></span>
<div><span style="word-wrap: break-word; font-family:"><font color="#596677">Spring 5核心原理与30个类手写实战+Spring Boot编程思想核心篇 pdf百度网盘 微服务软件架构
SpringBoot开发教程电子书pdf百度云下载&nbsp;<wbr>
&nbsp;<wbr></font><b style=""><font color="#FF3E0B">下载链接：</font></b></span><font color="#596677">http://www.137zw.com/thread-426-1-1.html</font>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft="" font-size:=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">《Spring
5核心原理与30个类手写实战》基于编程开发实践，不仅深度解析Spring
5的原理与新特性，更从环境准备、顶层结构设计、数据访问等方面一步步地推导出Spring的设计原理。在每个知识点上，均以大量的经典代码案例辅助讲解，使理论紧密联系实际。最后手写30个类，以体会Spring作者的创作过程，让每一位读者学以致用。</font></font></div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft="" font-size:=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">对于立志成为Java架构师的技术人员，以及对以Spring为核心的Java
Web开发感兴趣的计算机专业高校生、在职Java开发人员来说，本书是一本具备超强实战意义的技术升级指南。读者通过本书可以看源码不再“晕车”，轻松找到入口；系统学习设计思想，提高解决问题的效率；培养架构思维能力，以及自驱作者：小马哥
著</font></font></div>

Boot 工程中的代码结构、依赖关系等。在初步印象的前提下，进一步地深入探讨Spring Boot

<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">11.3.3 Spring
Boot事件ApplicationStartedEvent语义的变化 543</font></font></div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">11.3.4
执行CommandLineRunner和ApplicationRunner 548</font></font></div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">第12章
SpringApplication结束阶段 550</font></font></div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">12.1
SpringApplication正常结束 550</font></font></div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">12.2
SpringApplication异常结束 555</font></font></div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">12.2.1 Spring Boot异常处理
556</font></font></div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">12.2.2 错误分析报告器——FailureAnalysisReporter
562</font></font></div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">12.2.3
自定义实现FailureAnalyzer和FailureAnalysisReporter
564</font></font></div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">12.2.4 Spring Boot
2.0重构handleRunFailure和reportFailure方法 566</font></font></div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">12.2.5 Spring Boot
2.0的SpringBootExceptionRepor<wbr>ter接口 567</font></font></div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">第13章
Spring Boot应用退出 571</font></font></div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">13.1
Spring Boot应用正常退出 572</font></font></div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">13.1.1 ExitCodeGenerator Bean生成退出码
572</font></font></div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">13.1.2 ExitCodeGenerator Bean退出码使用场景
576</font></font></div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">13.2
Spring Boot应用异常退出 580</font></font></div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">13.2.1 ExitCodeGenerator异常使用场景
582</font></font></div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">13.2.2 ExitCodeExceptionMapper
Bean映射异常与退出码 587</font></font></div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">13.2.3 退出码用于SpringApplication异常结束
589</font></font></div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(89, 102, 119); font-family:" microsoft=""><font style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif" style="word-wrap: break-word;">13.3
小马哥有话说 594</font></font></div>
